"1/2 pound sliced bacon, diced","1  4- to 6-pound chicken, cut up","1/2 cup dry white wine (or 1/4 cup dry vermouth plus 1/4 cup water)","1/2 pound small white mushrooms","1 cup frozen small white onions, thawed","6  garlic cloves, chopped","3  sprigs fresh rosemary (or 1 tablespoon dried rosemary leaves)","1 teaspoon kosher salt","1/4 cup water","2 tablespoons cornstarch"